1. Kako bih znao da je točno cm *širok*? (How would I know it's exactly one cm *wide*?)
2. *Cm* po *cm*, izgradio je svoju karijeru. (Step by *step*, he built his career.)
3. Sliku morate odrezati za 2 *cm* sa svake strane. (You need to crop the image by 2 *cm* on each side.)
4. Molim vas da *cm* po *cm* provjerite dimenzije proizvoda. (Please check the product dimensions *inch by inch*.)
5. Ovaj konac ima debljinu od 2 *cm*. (This thread has a thickness of 2 *cm*.)
6. Sve što trebate je da *cm* po *cm* pratite upute na ekranu. (All you need to do is to follow the on-screen instructions *carefully*.)
7. Koliko *cm* si izrastao od prošle godine? (How many *cm* have you grown since last year?)
8. *Cm* po *cm*, slikar je nanosio boju na platno. (Stroke by *stroke*, the painter applied paint to the canvas.)
9. Ovaj traka je široka 5 *cm*. (This tape is 5 *cm* wide.)
10. Kupio sam novi tepih, dug je 2 metra i širok 1,5 *cm*. (I bought a new carpet, it's 2 meters long and 1.5 *cm* wide.)